description: Erection of a 3 storey building plus basement (25-27 Macaulay Road) to provide 7 residential units. Erection of a 2 storey building to the north of  MA building to provide 4 residential units.  Erection of an additional floor at the MA building and conversion to 19 residential units. Erection of a building at 31-33 Macaulay Road to provide 51 residential units. Erection of a 2 storey building to the rear of Nattrass House to provide 1 residential unit. Erection of a building on the former machine shop site to provide 3,248 sqm of Class B1. Refurbishment and part conversion of 29 Macaulay Road to provide 6 residential units. Conversion of the existing building situated between the MA building and the LETS site to provide 1 residential unit. Conversion of the former LETS site to 8 residential units and provision of 35 car parking spaces.
